ath11k: add hw_ops for pdev id to hw_mac mapping

pdev_id to hw_mac is different for ipq8074 and ipq6018
Below table has the mapping

pdev_id	ipq8074	ipq6018
-------	------- -------
  0		0	0
  1		2	1
  2		1	Not applicable

No functional changes. Compile tested only.

